cef provides CMake targets:

    find_package(CEF CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE CEF::CEF)

Individual targets are also available:

    CEF::wrapper  – static libcef_dll_wrapper
    CEF::lib      – prebuilt libcef shared library

The CEF resource directory (PAK files, locales) is available as:

    ${CEF_RESOURCE_DIR}
